Advanced Boot Options

This is an android applications, for rooted devices.
It enables the user to:
  1. shut down the phone.
  2. soft reboot the phone - restart OS.
  3. reboot.
  4. reboot into recovery - TWRP.
  5. reboot into bootloader.
  6. wipe data - factory reset. (not working, currently)
  
It Simple to use.
It is utilized firstly for Huawei P8 Lite: 
  only TWRP is available as a custom recovery (till now).
  Huawei's factory reset, not working while phone is rooted.
  It should work for other devices with TWRP, also.
  
It is mostly for personal use.
